t="拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 和比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)（摄影：Chelsea Lauren/Variety/Penske Media via Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lana-Del-Rey-and-Billie-Eilish-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lana-Del-Rey-and-Billie-Eilish-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lana-Del-Rey-and-Billie-Eilish-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lana-Del-Rey-and-Billie-Eilish-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lana-Del-Rey-and-Billie-Eilish-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lana-Del-Rey-and-Billie-Eilish-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Billie-Eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>表示，她与<a href="/artists/Lana-Del-Rey">Lana Del Rey</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">Coachella 的</a>合作“实际上是一种幻觉”，并补充说，如果没有她，“Ocean Eyes”“就不会存在”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lana-del-rey-live-coachella-2024-review-setlist-photos-3616916">Lana Del Rey 在 2024 年 Coachella 现场直播：独特的明星始终忠于自己</a></strong></li></ul><p>艾利什花时间在她的 Instagram 故事上反思了她在一年一度的音乐和艺术节周末之一德尔雷 (Del Rey) 的头条新闻中的意外亮相。</p><p>这位“坏家伙”歌手公开了她的首张单曲“Ocean Eyes”的创作，写道：“如果没有她，这首歌甚至不会存在”（根据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/billie-eilish-lana-del-rey-ocean-eyes-exists-1235659817/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>公告牌</em></a>）。她接着补充说，两人表演的二重唱“实际上是一种幻觉”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 和比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 在<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Coachella?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Coachella</a>演唱“Ocean Eyes”。 </p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a5.png" alt="🎥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/jeffmillerla?ref_src